Mahir Ünlü
Mahir Ünlü was born at Harput in 1926.
He was educated at Ankara, Gazi (Atatürk) Orman Çiftliği Onuncu Yıl Yatılı primary school(1938);Elazığ Lycee (1945), AÜ Language and History-Geography Faculty 'Turkish Language and Literature Department (1950), he was 'Turkish / Turkish Language and Literature teacher at various military schools in Turkey(1951–1971). After retiring he continued teaching literature at Darüşşafaka Lycee and Saint Joseph lycee at Istanbul (1971–1980). 
